        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "f333",
          "name": "How Timer Works Section",
          "fill": "#151922",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 8,
          "padding": 16,
          "cornerRadius": 8,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "fill": "#252B36",
            "thickness": 1
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "t330",
              "name": "desktopHowTitle",
              "content": "How the Diablo 4 World Boss Timer Works",
              "fill": "#F8FAFC",
              "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "t331",
              "name": "desktopHowBody1",
              "content": "A timer is only useful when players understand how much they can trust it. This tool uses a confirmed anchor, predicted rotation, local timezone conversion, manual review, and user feedback when needed.",
              "fill": "#71717A",
              "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "400",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "lineHeight": 1.4
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "t332",
              "name": "desktopHowBody2",
              "content": "Confirmed means the event has been reviewed or manually corrected. Predicted means the time was generated from the current schedule logic. Needs verification means there may be a timing, boss, or location issue that should be checked before you rely on it.",
              "fill": "#71717A",
              "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "400",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "lineHeight": 1.4
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "f344",
          "name": "FAQ Section",
          "fill": "#151922",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 8,
          "padding": 16,
          "cornerRadius": 8,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "fill": "#252B36",
            "thickness": 1
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "t334",
              "name": "desktopFaqTitle",
              "content": "Diablo 4 World Boss FAQ",
              "fill": "#F8FAFC",
              "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "f337",
              "name": "faq item",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 3,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "t335",
                  "name": "faqQuestion",
                  "content": "When is the next World Boss in Diablo 4?",
                  "fill": "#F8FAFC",
                  "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "t336",
                  "name": "faqAnswer",
                  "content": "The next World Boss is shown in the timer card at the top of the page. It includes the boss name, live countdown, local spawn time, region, location, nearest waypoint, and confidence status.",
                  "fill": "#71717A",
                  "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "400",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "lineHeight": 1.3
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "f340",
              "name": "faq item",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 3,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "t338",
                  "name": "faqQuestion",
                  "content": "How often do World Bosses spawn in Diablo 4?",
                  "fill": "#F8FAFC",
                  "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "t339",
                  "name": "faqAnswer",
                  "content": "The timer uses a 210-minute, or 3.5-hour, interval as the default prediction rule. Future events are still labeled by confidence status because seasonal updates or special events may affect the schedule.",
                  "fill": "#71717A",
                  "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "400",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "lineHeight": 1.3
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "f343",
              "name": "faq item",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 3,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "t341",
                  "name": "faqQuestion",
                  "content": "Can I get a reminder before a World Boss spawns?",
                  "fill": "#F8FAFC",
                  "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "t342",
                  "name": "faqAnswer",
                  "content": "Yes. The reminder panel can support warning times such as 5, 15, 30, or 60 minutes before the event. Browser notification permission should only be requested after you choose a reminder.",
                  "fill": "#71717A",
                  "fontFamily": "ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "400",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "lineHeight": 1.3
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
